00Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355a4a455560edaa951ec6b7e96d93b5c6edc611","tid":2299751,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a822c3be273b181b8cff480b4d52d57615073d48","tid":2299751,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"黑狗係商場撞路過市民入後門.gif"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"Yoho果單"},{"pid":"d3bb33724c6616c187710df37b8b4e2684074f38","tid":2299751,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2426d36b4b659aef18f49cc9359992f5cde5e419","tid":2299751,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c3f748f2017f45aba37331939e70d85f53d6af0","tid":2299751,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生更精彩啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"其實你哩啲人好可悲。<br />\n明知個社會係官官相衛，法治已死。<br />\n你都係小巿民，但又要扮到自己同個官係同一陣線。他朝君體也相同，你幫佢哋講嘢，佢哋都唔會俾着數你架。即使唔係你撞到鳩拉你嘅黑警同鳩判你嘅法官，你啲子子孫孫都會撞到，到時喊都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n希望第二時你家俾人抄，資產俾人沒收，被鳩告，以以同個官講：「我五毛/藍絲黎，同你哋好fd架。」"},{"pid":"fd99d903488b3a411ba3861289fb9b1562b71869","tid":2299751,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd645aa31459cd6cc428e8ba04c8f355470aea4","tid":2299751,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/DXAWOB3N2BCWXNVRLW2XT5CFRY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FDXAWOB3N2BCWXNVRLW2XT5CFRY%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=286d8d56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FDXAWOB3N2BCWXNVRLW2XT5CFRY%2F&h=ed2cb647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/DXAWOB3N2BCWXNVRLW2XT5CFRY/</a>"},{"pid":"bbe5d76ce4ad25b126d71cfed3cba189f8fb9086","tid":2299751,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:36:34.000Z","msg":"後香港年代"},{"pid":"8bf0be64cfd88e9d0d37c14160eb37e827f99af8","tid":2299751,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2426d36b4b659aef18f49cc9359992f5cde5e419","tid":2299751,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c3f748f2017f45aba37331939e70d85f53d6af0","tid":2299751,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人生更精彩啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"其實你哩啲人好可悲。<br />\n明知個社會係官官相衛，法治已死。<br />\n你都係小巿民，但又要扮到自己同個官係同一陣線。他朝君體也相同，你幫佢哋講嘢，佢哋都唔會俾着數你架。即使唔係你撞到鳩拉你嘅黑警同鳩判你嘅法官，你啲子子孫孫都會撞到，到時喊都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n希望第二時你家俾人抄，資產俾人沒收，被鳩告，以以同個官講：「我五毛/藍絲黎，同你哋好fd架。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被害妄想症發作？"},{"pid":"